  <brief_title>Transanal Haemorrhoidal Dearterialisation Versus Stapler Haemorrhoidopexy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transanal Haemorrhoidal Dearterialisation Versus Stapler Haemorrhoidopexy. A Randomized Trial With Long-term Follow-up</official_title>
